<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The only behavioural difference is that this class sets the type properly.</db:para>
<db:para>This class also features a <db:link xlink:href="qtapsensor.xml#reading">reading</db:link>() function that returns a <db:link xlink:href="qtapreading.xml">QTapReading</db:link> instead of a <db:link xlink:href="qsensorreading.xml">QSensorReading</db:link>.</db:para>
<db:para>For details about how the sensor works, see <db:link xlink:href="qtapreading.xml">QTapReading</db:link>.</db:para>
